data.description: Light, bright, and spacious townhome in Alta Views! This 2 bed, 2.5 bath, 1780 sq ft. townhome features an open living concept in the kitchen, living room, and dining areas. Generous entryway and half bath are located on the main floor. Upstairs you will find a vaulted master bedroom with en-suite bathroom. Large loft area in master allows for additional sleeping quarters or office/storage space. Second bedroom also contains en-suite bathroom and laundry is located in the hallway. Oversized 2 car garage with plenty of storage. Quick access to the Whitefish River walking and biking paths. Appreciate easy living with lawn care, cable, internet, and snow plowing all included in the HOA fees. Also included is access to the clubhouse with hot tubs, gym, and billiards area located right out your back door. Minutes to downtown Whitefish, Whitefish Mountain Resort, and Glacier National Park!
